<F P=100> North Korea </F>
<H3> <TI>   Iranian, Tanzanian Visitors Arrive in Pyongyang </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Iranian, Tanzanian Visitors Arrive in Pyongyang </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK0905114094 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1049 GMT 9 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK0905114094 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, May 9 (KCNA) -- A delegation of the 
Iran-Korea friendship parliamentary group headed by member of 
parliament Khodakaram Jalali, head of the Agricultural 
Commission of the Islamic Consultative Assembly and chairman of 
the group, arrived here today. 
  It was met at the airport by Chairman of the Korea-Iran 
friendship parliamentary group and Vice-Chairman of the Supreme 
People's Assembly Paek In-chun, Secretary General of the group 
and Deputy to the Supreme People's Assembly Yu Kyu-tong and the 
charge d'affaires ad interim of the Iranian Embassy in Pyongyang. 
  A delegation of the Tanzanian Youth Union headed by its 
General Secretary Sukuwa S. Sukuwa arrived here today. 

</TEXT>

