  [Text] Hanoi VNA May 10 -- A Vietnamese delegation led by 
Governor of the Vietnam State Bank Cao Si Kiem has attended the 
annual conference of the Asian Development Bank (ADB) held in 
Nice France. 
  The conference was attended by representatives of ADB's 55 
members, international monetary organizations, major world banks 
and investment companies. 
  Addressing the event, Governor Cao Si Kiem expressed the 
