yen-dollar rate at an appropriate level and promote political, 
administrative and economic reforms. 
  Hayami asked Hata to follow the reform-oriented policies 
pursued by former Prime Minister Morihiro Hosokawa and appealed 
for a national election under a new electoral system after 
summer. 

