<H4>    Resistance Leader Asks Portugal for Help </H4>

<F P=102> LD0905154994 Lisbon RDP Antena 1 Radio Network in Portuguese 
1700 GMT 8 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0905154994 </F>
<F P=104>  Lisbon RDP Antena 1 Radio Network </F>
