  [Text] Three thousand winning candidates in the recently 
concluded village elections have already been proclaimed by the 
Comelec [Commission on Elections]. These were registered by the 
Comelec as part of the first batch of winning candidates. They 
represent more than 300 of the 41,000 villages in the whole 
