<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Tokyo, May 12 KYODO -- Japanese Trade Minister 
Eijiro Hata on Thursday [13 May] pledged that Tokyo would make 
efforts to deepen its ties with China. Japan should do its 
utmost to make its ties with China "fruitful" while reflecting 
on the recent controversial remark by a Japanese cabinet 
minister, International Trade and Industry Minister Hata told a 
