at the invitation of Senior General Than Shwe, prime minister of 
the Union of Myanmar. 
  The visiting prime minister, Mr. Vo Van Kiet, his wife, 
Madame Vo Van Kiet, and his delegation were welcomed by Prime 
Minister Sr. Gen. Than Shwe and his wife, Daw Kyaing Kyaing; 
General Maung Aye, deputy chairman of the State Law and Order 
Restoration Council [SLORC], and his wife; Lt. Gen. Tin Tun, 
deputy prime minister; Lt. Gen. Khin Nyunt, SLORC secretary-1; 
Lt. Gen. Tin U, SLORC secretary-2, and his wife; Lt. Gen. Myo 
Nyunt, minisiter of religious affairs; Brigadier General Myo 
Thant, minister of information; U Ohn Gyaw, minister of foreign 
affairs, and his wife; U Nyunt Swe, deputy foreign minister, and 
his wife; U Aye, Myanmar ambassador to the SRV, and his wife; 
