leader of the diplomatic corps in Myanmar; senior diplomats from 
foreign embassies; and the staff of the Vietnamese Embassy. 
Students greeted the visitors by waving the flags of two 
countries and shouted slogans of friendship between two 
countries. [passage on welcoming ceremony omitted] 
  Vietnamese Prime Minister Mr. Vo Van Kiet is accompanied by 
a 
37- member delegation that include his wife, Madame Vo Van Kiet; 
