BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, May 12 (KCNA) -- Comrade Kim Il-song, 
general secretary of the Central Committee of the Workers' Party 
of Korea, today sent a message of greetings to Henri Konan Bedie 
upon his election as president of the Central Committee of the 
Democratic Party of Cote d'Ivoire. 
  Comrade Kim Il-song wished him greater success in his 
responsible work for the strengthening and development of the 
party and for the prosperity of the Cote d'Ivoire people. 

</TEXT>

